Rating: 4
This is an extremely version of a French classic--not cloyingly sweet and where all the ingredients have distinct an individual flavorings. I've made it several times to rave reviews (including a test on some very culinarily fussy French friends)and friends who begged for the recipe and tried it themselves had similar triumphs at table. I substituted native Northern Spys for the Granny Smiths.